<ul>
<li>
3-5 years of agency or corporate marketing experience</li>
<li>
Extremely proficient in Photoshop and Illustrator (Fireworks, Dreamweaver and Flash knowledge a plus)</li>
<li>
Proven conceptualization skills that can translate to the web effectively</li>
<li>
Proven execution of web design best practices and modern standards</li>
<li>
An extreme eye for detail</li>
<li>
A kick ass portfolio</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Your duties will include (but may not be limited to):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Creating wireframes based on client requirements that utilize standard web user experience best practices.</li>
